Compile
----------
Run `make` (it runs `sbt compile`)


Usage
-------
First run the emulator:

./nEmulator 9991 host2 9994 9993 host3 9992 1 0.2 0

Then the receiver:

./receiver.sh host1 9993 9994 <output file>

Then the sender:

./sender.sh host1 9991 9992 <input file>


Source code
------------

Source code is in `/src/main/scala`.

Compiling info
----------------
* This program was tested on `ubuntu1404-008`, `ubuntu1404-004` and `ubuntu1404-002`

* make version: GNU Make 3.81

* java version: 1.8.0_91

* sbt version: 0.13.12

* scala version: 2.10.6
